rComments: Very fast speaker, sometimes mumbles. Does not let you use phones, laptops or any electronic devices in class. Very little homework. DO NOT skip class.

i usually dont do these ratings but I HATED THIS PROF! Definitely the worst professor I've ever had!! Speaks too fast, makes you feel bad for making him repeat and ask questions, makes classes mandatory and talk about tough grader. AVOID. AT. ALL. COST.
He is a very hard marking prof.  It is important to attend his lectures because he gives important exam details in class.  He also speaks very quickly!

Horrible professor. Makes you write notes by hand, speaks too fast, and hates repeating things  (even though he's talking so fast he's tripping over his words. Exam material is not representative of the course as a whole- very specific because he wasnts to be a tough guy... get the sense he doesn't want people to do well.

Bon professeur, mais il faut travailler pour avoir une bonne notes dans le cours si vous étudier vous allez bien faire.. Il y a eu beaucoup de faillites dans la classe car beaucoup ne prennent pas sa au sérieux.

Bon professeur, (ceux qui l'évalue de façons négative c'est probablement parce que la gestion n'est pas dans leur avenir...). Même si on doit prendre des notes à la main, le cours reste intéressant (pour ceux qui aime la gestion). La matière est facile à apprendre si on écoute le professeur. Il explique très bien !!!

worst prof ever. doesn't let you bring laptops yet makes you take notes to the point where your hands are about to break off. calls out his student if they are late, or even say a word in class. and he refuses to help his students if he thinks they don't pay attention in class, even if they are! if you can avoid him, DO IT!

Very boring teacher but still knows what he's talking about. If you like to take notes the old school way... take his class. No laptops allowed and lots of notes. AVOID
Il presente bien la matiere et il est tres dynamique.
Prof qui connait bien sa matiere.  les examens ne sont pas trop difficiles, mais il faut tout apprendre

Il explique bien sa matière.  Le premier examen e été représentatif de la matière vue en classe mais l'examen finale ne l'était pas du tout!!! Pour ce qui est du projet, ce n'était pas clair ce qu'il fallait faire... il croit que les gens copient, surtout pour le projet...si ce n'est pas un cours obligatoire, eviter ce prof.

If you want to learn nothing, go to his class. Maybe its the material he has to teach, maybe it has nothing to do with him, but this class is a complete waste of time. Also, don't talk durnig class, he will stare at you. The main reason why this class is boring is that he just reads off the powerpoint slides... typical ADM class.

Cool prof but don't mess with him. Knows his stuff very well so he expects the same.  Exams are fair if you attended ALL classes, printed ALL his slides and read ALL his textbook and ALL of his extra references. So make sure you know everything!
